data.description: Step into a slice of paradise with this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven set on the serene shores of Lake Granbury. The open and inviting interior combines relaxed vibes with modern comforts, creating the perfect backdrop for both lazy weekend mornings and fun-filled evenings. Large windows ensure that you're always connected to those lake views, even when you're indoors. Venture outside to find a welcoming backyard crafted for enjoyment. Whether you're lounging with a good book, hosting a BBQ, or gearing up for a day on the water, this space has it all. And with a boat dock, aquatic adventures are just steps away. Here's your chance to enjoy the best of lakeside living at a price that doesn’t come around often!
